metadata.name: Tablet of mankind
metadata.description:
It captures the idea of a separate world hurtling through the cosmos, with a life and energy of its own, while simultaneously portraying the inner world of the individual, simmering with its own unique experiences and emotions. It invites the viewer to contemplate the interconnectedness of our personal worlds with the grandeur of the universe, and to consider the ways in which our individual journeys are shaped by the infinite possibilities of the cosmos.
